jei.pokefood.mixing_info:
Some pastries can be made in a mixer, the resulting item will change based on the flavors of the ingredients used.

Poké-Puffs need 2 berries and 2 other ingredients (like fruits). The amount of flavors will change the resulting quality

Poffin dough need 2 berries, 1 milk bucket and 1 other ingredients in the same way the poké-puffs does.

"Replacement powders" can be used in place of berries.

jei.pokefood.cheese_making_info:
Cheese is made by adding a curd bag into a cheese mold.

The biome's temperature will change what cheese you'll get in the end.

jei.pokefood.wrapped_burger_info:
A burger can be wrapped by having paper in one hand and a burger in the other and right clicking. 

To open a wrapped burger, just right click with it in hand, you'll also get the paper back.
